pull something out of your ass.

00:28.250 --> 00:30.458
- What magic shows
did you go to?

00:30.458 --> 00:32.667
- I need a pet name for Helen.

00:32.667 --> 00:35.500
- Really?
Pet names already?

00:35.500 --> 00:37.417
- I know.

00:37.417 --> 00:40.667
It's like we're on some kind
of accelerated lesbian calendar.

00:40.667 --> 00:43.000
